image_analysis.description: A photograph of a bathroom interior. The room features a white vanity with a reddish-brown marble countertop and a white sink. A white towel is folded on the counter. Above the vanity is a mirror with a dark frame and a decorative black wall sconce with three small lampshades. The walls are covered in a vertical striped wallpaper with pink, yellow, and blue/grey tones. To the left is a glass-enclosed shower stall with brown marble walls. A white toilet is partially visible behind the vanity. The floor is covered in a light-colored patterned carpet or rug. A white towel lies on the floor in front of the shower.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot taken from a doorway perspective.
